{
  "stem": "24625.1",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "All kind of adventures that happened to us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had a friend over there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Not a Jew, a goyem from the village.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I forgot the name.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But he had a factory from cigars.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The father, he was making little cigars.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we went-- a bunch of guys of us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were wearing those golf pants, you know, that go down there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we went there, and while they were not looking, we filled up our pants with cigars.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] Then with this we came back, and then we went to the peasants and we exchanged cigars for eggs, for butter, for bread.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we bought a dinner.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We distributed for all the kids.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'm telling you, we organized ourselves.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The bigger kids, we were very, very well organized.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We used to go to the butcher, and we could buy meat without the stamps-- black market.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But it used to cost maybe 10 times more than the regular way.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we came in and we said, we want to have, let's see-- for $1 a small piece of meat on the black market.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But the guy didn't have the meat the same place that he had the other, so he had to go in the back to get this other meat.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "While he went in other the back, we went and we stole stamps.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And when he came back, we say, we changed our mind.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We don't want this.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Maybe we're going to buy with stamps, and we bought for cheaper.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
